{"tid":496838,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嚴詞反駁批評　林鄭：政府不會做損害市民工作","createTime":"2017-12-12T06:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-13T03:31:17.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":53,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"c40d8e569decef60b9b7426f1a318439125e17ff","tid":496838,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:16:55.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嚴詞反駁批評　林鄭：政府不會做損害市民工作</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171212/s00001/d6b773dde3ebbb26fe126b91a942c85c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171212%2Fs00001%2Fd6b773dde3ebbb26fe126b91a942c85c.jpg&h=b218ceee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n立法會修改《議事規則》爭議持續。特首林鄭月娥早上出席行政會議前對傳媒表示，修改《議事規則》與23條立法沒有關係。針對有意見指修改《議事規則》令立法會失去阻止政府做損害市民事情的權力，她反駁稱「政府不會做損害市民的事」。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥指出，「我做了政府37年，這個政府無論上屆、這一屆，都不會做損害市民的工作。工作或許未滿足所有市民期望，但（政府）絕對不會做傷害市民的工作」。她批評用這些藉口抗拒修改《議事規則》，是完全不適當。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171212/s00001/1513046744435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171212%2Fs00001%2F1513046744435&d=xVqc45u1mH9EvxO4nUbrKbDFWuQMdHqkD4FeOi%2BWxPk%3D&h=66edce4a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20171212%2Fs00001%2F1513046744435&h=750a7408\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20171212/s00001/1513046744435</a>"},{"pid":"8c1b8aa7d070220f5d2df03754cb825f22759ef8","tid":496838,"uid":47359,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T06:24:11.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">最衰都係梁耀忠</span><br />\n<br />\n2016-2017年度立會傑出柒頭: 梁耀忠<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/456906/2?ref=android\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/456906/2?ref=android</a><br />\n<br />\nLIHKG @ Android"},{"pid":"